      AfricanElephantDatabase.org is the online home of the African Elephant Database,
      maintained by the [IUCN SSC African Elephant Specialist Group (AfESG)](http://www.iucn.org/african_elephant).

      AfricanElephantDatabase.org presents data from past [African Elephant Status Reports](report),
      as well as more recent survey data reported to the AfESG. Data on this web site is made available under a
      [Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlikeÂ license](http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0).


      Request Data
      ----------------

      To request spatial and tabular data from the current and previous African Elephant Status Reports,
      please email [#{AedEnv.REQUEST_FORM_SUBMITTED_TO_EMAIL}](mailto:#{AedEnv.REQUEST_FORM_SUBMITTED_TO_EMAIL})
      with a brief summary of the data you are requesting and the intended use of the data.

