      Technology
      ----------------

      AfricanElephantDatabase.org is an Open Source software project.
      AfricanElephantDatabase.org was created with PostgreSQL, PostGIS, Ruby, and Ruby on Rails.
      Every aspect of the database is powered by free and open source software.
